desc_long								关于这款游戏							In a ferocious Arctic storm, distress signals are sent from a mysterious Russian whaler. As leading Coast Guard veteran Tom Hansen, you board to investigate  and discover unthinkable horrors lurking beneath the ship's bloodstained decks.										Brave dangerous waters: Rocked by huge breakers, you must steady your nerves  and aim  to evade a watery grave.					Keep your bearings: Battle against increasingly mutated enemies in treacherous, unstable environments.					Unleash a torrent of weapons: Create fatal traps and use shotguns, flame throwers, or any object you can find to survive.						
